oretical analysis, the algorithm to find the constrained optimal policy is\npresented for the finite state space scenario. In addition, heuristic policies\nwith low-complexity are given for the general state space. Finally, simulations\nare performed under these policies to demonstrate the effectiveness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Nov 2012 07:47:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 2 Dec 2012 08:16:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 20 Dec 2012 03:16:11 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 26 Dec 2012 07:41:48 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 28 Feb 2013 05:44:20 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Thu, 28 Nov 2013 13:47:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-02"}
