ally, we compare the DFT+U results with\nexchange couplings obtained from hybrid functionals. It is argued that\nanisotropic interactions should be included in DFT+U if the results are to be\nproperly compared with those from hybrid functionals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Nov 2012 14:46:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-11-26"}
